
## Description of Drivability Problems  


Description of Drivability Problems- STUMBLE: Mildly irregular performance during acceleration.- HESITATION: A dip or flat spot in performance just after the accelerator pedal is depressed.- SURGE: Continuous irregular performance during cruising.  

